soon as possible on this and his
position on that conversation.

00:29.266 --> 00:30.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
QUESTION: Right, but
what is he waiting for?

00:30.933 --> 00:32.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
What's the delay?

00:32.433 --> 00:33.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SEAN SPICER: He's waiting --
he's not waiting for anything.

00:33.900 --> 00:35.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
When he's ready to further
discuss it, he will.

00:35.866 --> 00:38.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Spicer also
wouldn't say if Attorney General
Jeff Sessions will invoke

00:38.566 --> 00:42.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
