guilty today to a misdemeanor
charge, and was sentenced
to 40 hours of community

04:47.500 --> 04:49.500 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
service.

04:49.500 --> 04:53.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He will also attend 20 hours
of anger management counseling
and pay a fine of $385.

04:55.300 --> 05:00.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A Pennsylvania jury has
begun deliberating in Bill
Cosby's sexual assault trial.

05:01.233 --> 05:03.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The defense rested
abruptly today.

05:03.366 --> 05:07.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Cosby himself, accompanied
by his wife for the first
time, declined to testify.

05:09.933 --> 05:12.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
His defense team argued the
comedian and his accuser had
a consensual relationship.

05:14.166 --> 05:16.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Prosecutors argued that
Cosby drugged the woman.

05:16.433 --> 05:21.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In Orlando, Florida, today,
they remembered the deadliest
mass shooting in modern U.S.

05:21.900 --> 05:23.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
history.

05:23.966 --> 05:27.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A gunman, Omar Mateen, killed
49 people at a gay nightclub
last June 12, before police

05:29.566 --> 05:31.066 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
killed him.

05:31.066 --> 05:33.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He'd pledged allegiance to
the Islamic State group.

05:33.866 --> 05:38.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This morning, a vigil
began at 2:00 a.m., the
same hour as the rampage.

05:38.533 --> 05:42.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Names of the victims were read
aloud, and hundreds carried
candles and laid flowers.

05:42.866 --> 05:47.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BUDDY DYER, Mayor of Orlando,
Florida: We are not here to
relive the horror of that

05:47.066 --> 05:48.066 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
day.

05:48.066 --> 05:50.166 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
We're here for a
greater purpose.

05:50.166 --> 05:53.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We're here to remember the
innocent lives that were lost.

05:53.600 --> 05:55.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We're here to honor them.

05:55.733 --> 06:00.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Orlando has been anointed to
show the world how to combat
hatred and evil and promote

06:01.133 --> 06:03.133 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
quality and embrace diversity.

06:03.133 --> 06:05.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And we don't just have the
opportunity to do this.

06:05.733 --> 06:09.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We now have the
responsibility to do this.

06:09.333 --> 06:14.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
